# IDP Management System — AI Spec

**Generate code strictly following this spec.** Do not add features not listed here. Ask for clarification before deviating.

## Stack & Phase

- Next.js 15 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind, shadcn/ui, Prisma, Vercel Postgres
- PoC / 1-day build
- Auth: Mock login — HTTP-only cookie with `userId`, no OAuth/JWT

## Roles

| Role | Label | Scope |
|------|-------|-------|
| `EMPLOYEE` | Employee | Own IDP only |
| `HR_COMPANY` | HR (Company) | Own company + subsidiaries |
| `HR_GROUP` | HR (Group) | All companies |

## Structure

- `src/app/` — layout, page, dashboard, idp, api/auth/logout
- `src/components/` — layout (Navbar, DeadlineBanner), login, idp (IdpForm), dashboard (StatsCards, SubmissionTable, SubmissionChart)
- `src/lib/` — prisma, session, utils
- `src/actions/` — auth, idp, dashboard
- `src/types/index.ts` — shared types, Zod schemas, ActionResult

## Key Rules

- **Auth:** `getSession()`, `setSession()`, `clearSession()` from `@/lib/session.ts`. Auth check in each page's Server Component.
- **Server Actions:** Return `ActionResult<T>`, validate session first, never throw.
- **DeadlineBanner (3 priorities):** 1) Overdue (red), 2) Missing current quarter (amber), 3) Current TODO (blue).
- **Database:** Prisma schema with Company, User, IdpSubmission. Seed: 3 companies, 5 users, 2 overdue IDPs.
- **shadcn components:** button, card, badge, alert, select, textarea, toast, table, avatar, separator

## Key Types

- `IdpFormSchema`, `IdpFormInput`, `ActionResult<T>`, `BannerState`, `DashboardStats`, `SubmissionRow`

## Out of Scope (Do NOT implement)

- Real auth (OAuth, NextAuth, JWT), email notifications, file upload, edit/delete IDP, pagination beyond 50, i18n, dark mode, tests

